    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In &quot;<strong>Pryizm</strong>,&quot; players assume the role of elite soldiers undergoing rigorous training in an AI-controlled space prison. The ultimate purpose of this prison remains ambiguous, with hints of ulterior motives behind the AI's seemingly sadistic training methods. The prison sits atop a portal leading to a hell-like dimension, introducing elements of horror and mystery. When a soldier dies, the AI resurrects them using advanced cloning technology, ensuring the training—and suffering—continues indefinitely.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter <strong>Pryizm</strong> and take on the role of a soldier vying for glory in combat.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arcade Shooter Gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Custom Lobbies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team, Capture the Flag, and Deathmatch Game Modes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quick Movement Based Combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Futuristic Sci-Fi Theme and Setting</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Coming Soon</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Matchmaking</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More Game Modes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More Weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More Levels</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Images</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262110/extras/eb2137db7ed9155178211e322bedbd5c.avif?t=1758936463\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262110/extras_big/eb2137db7ed9155178211e322bedbd5c.webp?t=1758936463 width=1560 height=849 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find yourself in a futuristic environment simulated to train the most advanced of soldiers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262110/extras/dfd243a73483c0f3aaa87fdd738ec584.avif?t=1758936463\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262110/extras_big/dfd243a73483c0f3aaa87fdd738ec584.webp?t=1758936463 width=1560 height=881 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Custom lobbies with multiple game mode options.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262110/extras/03fa2b812e6fa2096980ce9e66c79be4.avif?t=1758936463\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262110/extras_big/03fa2b812e6fa2096980ce9e66c79be4.webp?t=1758936463 width=1560 height=906 /></span></p>",
